Vladimír Guma Kulhánek (born 4 September 1944 in Prague, Protectorate of Bohemia and Moravia; now Czech Republic) is a Czech rock bass guitarist.
Now, he is member of T4, November 2nd, Energit and supergroup called Kulhánek/Holeček/Razím/Kowacz.
